[22-Apr-2020 13:31:39 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[22-Apr-2020 13:31:39 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[24-Apr-2020 21:25:30 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[30-Apr-2020 12:40:01 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[30-Apr-2020 12:40:01 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[03-May-2020 19:21:05 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[03-May-2020 19:37:52 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[16-May-2020 20:06:21 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[16-May-2020 20:29:59 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;
[16-May-2020 20:30:09 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_id` = 4 || `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = 4) AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;

[17-May-2020 17:39:05 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[18-May-2020 14:00:53 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,

[18-May-2020 18:16:38 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_code` LIKE '%promot%' OR `tbl_product`.`title` LIKE '%promot%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_type` LIKE '%promot%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_key` LIKE '%promot%' OR `PR`.`title` LIKE '%promot%' OR `GP`.`title` LIKE '%promot%') AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[01-Jun-2020 13:35:52 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;
[01-Jun-2020 13:35:57 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

[02-Jun-2020 14:14:02 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;
[02-Jun-2020 14:14:08 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_code` LIKE '%Floor Graphics Decals, Warning%' OR `tbl_product`.`title` LIKE '%Floor Graphics Decals, Warning%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_type` LIKE '%Floor Graphics Decals, Warning%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_key` LIKE '%Floor Graphics Decals, Warning%' OR `PR`.`title` LIKE '%Floor Graphics Decals, Warning%' OR `GP`.`title` LIKE '%Floor Graphics Decals, Warning%') AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[02-Jun-2020 14:14:08 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
